message.body: I just realized how jealous i actually am. Whats wrong with me?
Yes. I do not know. I think i have to know my own worth before i can compare
Or maybe i Shouldnt compare at all

Sorry I fell asleep. No there's no need to compare nor any gain but there is a need to know your own worth as much as possible without Phillips words. You are a universe (and an ant...) of your own talents and loves and needs and it would be simplifying a beautiful complicated constellation to compare it.
